 //flex box

 css felxbox(flexible box layout)is a layout model designed to create complex and flexible layouts more efficiently than traditional models.

 syntax
    display:flex;
*display flex
*felxdirection

row:
    justify content -> x direction
    allign items -> y direction
 
column:
    justify content -> y direction
    allign items -> x direction
    
justify content for row
to make space on parent (space-around)
to make space even on parent (space-even)
space between only on parent not on ending (space-between)

allign items for row
 to make center (center)

 justify content for column
 same as row

 allign item for column
 same as row

 flex-wrap:wrap;